&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
== sanity test 254: Check changelog size ================= 07:19:21 (1634627961)
CMD: trevis-205vm4 /usr/sbin/lctl get_param -n mdd..changelog_size
trevis-205vm4: error: get_param: param_path &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;mdd&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//changelog_size&apos;&lt;/span&gt;: No such file or directory
&lt;/span&gt;pdsh@trevis-205vm1: trevis-205vm4: ssh exited with exit code 2

